videos.headline: Cunningham connects with Atwell early for 33-yard TD
videos.description: Tutu Atwell comes up with a quick grab in coverage on Louisville's first drive for a 33-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-play (Cunningham connects with Atwell early for 33-yard TD) 2019/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Rose powers through Louisville's defense for a TD
videos.description: Kentucky's RB Asim Rose finds an open hole and takes it to the house to put the Wildcats up 7-6.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-play (Rose powers through Louisville's defense for a TD) 2019/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Smoke sets up TD with 70-yard run
videos.description: Kavosiey Smoke finds the sidelines then cuts back to the middle of the field for a 70-yard run, setting fellow RB Lynn Bowden Jr. up for an easy six-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-play (Smoke sets up TD with 70-yard run) 2019/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kentucky's Griffin comes up with crazy INT
videos.description: Micale Cunningham launches a long ball that bounces off of multiple people before landing in Jordan Griffin's hands for an unbelievable interception.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-play (Kentucky's Griffin comes up with crazy INT) 2019/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hawkin turns pitch play into 56-yard TD
videos.description: Javian Hawkins reads a pitch play perfectly, finding an open hole and then cutting back across the field for a 56-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-play (Hawkin turns pitch play into 56-yard TD) 2019/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bowden takes it to the house for a 46-yard TD
videos.description: Lynn Bowden Jr. takes off after a good block on the line and doesn't stop until he hits pay dirt for a 46-yard Kentucky TD.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-play (Bowden takes it to the house for a 46-yard TD) 2019/11/30 ESHEET
